description: This common Sakura purrs with a rating of 15, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 45, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 2 for East, Nine Lives for South, and Leverage for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [45 Votes, Common]
